        public EntityPlayer getActor()
        The initiator of actions. for very critical errors you can also just send the error messages here, bypassing any filter that getChatter() might have. You might want to use StructureLibAPI.addThrottledChat(Object, EntityPlayer, IChatComponent, short) to help reduce spam.
